            &lt;h1 class=&quot;fs-1 fw-bold text-capitalize fw-normal p-3 m-0 d-inline-block&quot; style=&quot;color: var(--theme-orange);&quot;&gt;Scientific Symposia in Frontline Areas of Research&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
